title: Vista Ultimate - SP1 - 32bit 64bit x86 x64 - Activated - English
description:
Windows Vista Ultimate with Service Pack 1.

Includes both 32bit and 64bit versions.

English language only, sorry.

Fully activated and can be updated from Microsoft.

This is an ISO file so just double click to burn to a DVD-R.

Is bootable for a clean install or can be used to upgrade.

Does not need a Product Key or anything else.

Once installation is complete, Vista will be fully activated.



If activation fails for any reason, you will be notified and you will be asked if you want to try other methods of activation. There are between 2 and 5 methods of activation (depending on your machine).



OEM logos will be installed automatically. If your machine is custom built, an Intel or AMD logo will be installed instead.




The activator has been embedded deep in to Vista to ensure a smooth installation.
Activation occurs during installation and not after.
The activator deletes it's self leaving no trace.
As soon as you see the Desktop, you're ready to go.
